====成员不止一个地区的国家====
共有十个成员国在不止一个地区拥有会员资格。 两个国家是四个不同地区的成员，八个国家是两个地区的成员。 这些国家及其地区如下：
{{columns-list|colwidth=22em|
*{{flag|France}} (Regions I, III, IV, and VI)
*{{flag|United Kingdom}} (Regions I, IV, V, and VI)
*{{flag|Colombia}} (Regions III and IV)
*{{flag|Kazakhstan}} (Regions II and VI)
*{{flag|Netherlands}} (Regions IV and VI)
*{{flag|Portugal}} (Regions I and VI)
*{{flag|Russian Federation}} (Regions II and VI)
*{{flag|Spain}} (Regions I and VI)
*{{flag|United States of America}} (Regions IV and V)
*{{flag|Venezuela}} (Regions III and IV)
